metadata.name: DUNGSINO
metadata.description:
Welcome to DUNGSINO
DUNGSINO is the place where Dungjukas come to gamble using onions, Ether and Dung coins in their bets.
Certainly, some Dungjuka will losing all their onions. And the big prize here is Ether. However, Dungjuka don't know what to do with it.


MP4 : 2500x1666 / 25 FPS
Artwork, Animated, Music by DFifty
